room_title: Escape room "The Elf Cabin" by Unlock Escape Rooms in Fresno
room_description:
Santa is as old as The Ages — so are the elves that make all the perfect presents just in time for Christmas!  But what do the elves  do on Christmas Eve when Santa is out delivering those precious gifts to all the good girls and boys? The elves take a break, of course!  A few might even decide to retire to a quiet place in the woods, where no one will see traces of their magical footprints!

You are lucky this year… you have stumbled upon an elf’s tiny cabin. Has Santa forgotten his most devoted elf, Elvin? See what elves do in their spare time. Do they have a favorite story? Do they still make toys? Do elves keep treasures that you and I have only ever dreamed of?

…Take it all in before Elvin returns!
